564
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:13,680
Didn't you read all the files?

565
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,440
I didn't read about Ma Jincai.

566
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:21,400
Ding Baoyuan ran away at that time.

567
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:27,750
Get in the car.

568
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:30,200
Editor-in-chief, Zhao,
made a deal with me

569
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:34,920
to hold a book launch in the town

570
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,240
for 1,000 people.

571
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,240
This must be the first time

572
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:40,480
