573
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:41,880
What do you think if it sells...

574
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:42,790
Dad, I want to see the toys.

575
00:27:42,790 --> 00:27:44,350
Why do you want toys again?

576
00:27:44,350 --> 00:27:45,350
We have so many toys at home.

577
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:47,070
Silly woman!

578
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,960
Are you going
to do your homework or not?

579
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,270
Zhuangzhuang, go ahead and pick it out.

580
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:53,110
I'll pay when you're done.

581
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:58,070
Don't let Zhuangzhuang

582
00:27:58,270 --> 00:27:59,880
call you Dad when we're outside.

583
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:03,880
What's wrong?
You look so glum all the way.

584
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:06,070
Those two cops were here

585
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,440
for Ding Baoyuan's case.

586
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:12,030
He's been saying he's innocent
for five or six years in prison,

587
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:14,590
and I didn't expect an investigation
to actually take place.

588
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,590
He's been locked up for so long,

589
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:19,240
what's the use of appealing now?

590
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:23,920
Don't frown.

591
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,830
What are you doing? We're on the street.

592
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,030
Have you picked it out yet?

593
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:33,240
Which one?

594
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:34,070
A car.

595
00:28:34,070 --> 00:28:35,000
Okay. How much?

596
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:35,790
20 yuan.

597
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:36,440
Here you go.

598
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:39,830
Let's go.

599
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,030
Stop there.

600
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:44,790
Walk after five seconds.

601
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:49,720
My boy.

602
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,030
Zhuangzhuang.

603
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,270
Here it is.

604
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:11,520
Ma Jincai!

605
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:13,000
Stop there, Ma Jincai!

606
00:29:13,230 --> 00:29:13,840
Ma Jincai!

607
00:29:13,840 --> 00:29:14,390
Stop there, Ma Jincai!

608
00:29:14,390 --> 00:29:15,630
Let me pull up my trousers.

609
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:16,270
Don't run.

610
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:17,600
Go back. Why are you chasing after me?

611
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,600
Why are you chasing after me?

612
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:19,350
Your husbands will break your legs.

613
00:29:19,350 --> 00:29:19,950
Jincai!

614
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:22,760
Chen. Officer Chen.

615
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:24,000
Listen, the cop is here.

616
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:24,550
He'll arrest you guys.

617
00:29:24,550 --> 00:29:25,390
What are they doing?

618
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:26,520
Go back.

619
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:28,390
Your husbands will break your legs. Go.

620
00:29:28,390 --> 00:29:29,190
A view of the village.

621
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,190
He harassed them.

622
00:29:34,030 --> 00:29:34,990
What have you done?

623
00:29:35,360 --> 00:29:37,070
They took advantage of me, Chen.

624
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,640
When did you come back?

625
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:41,510
Watch out, their husbands
will break your legs.

626
00:29:41,710 --> 00:29:42,510
Break your legs.

627
00:29:42,840 --> 00:29:43,990
They harassed me.

628
00:29:44,470 --> 00:29:45,160
Have one.

629
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:45,880
No.

630
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:47,680
I'll go inside

631
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:49,640
and have some tea.

632
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:51,120
I don't have good tea.

633
00:29:52,470 --> 00:29:54,440
She said I harassed her

634
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,840
and she was struggling?

635
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:57,360
That's what Sun Caiyun said.

636
00:29:58,750 --> 00:29:59,920
That's true.

637
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,120
I'm warning you, Ma Jincai.

638
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:05,550
It's a murder case.
You want to be involved?

639
00:30:05,790 --> 00:30:06,230
Chen.

640
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,070
Chen.

641
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,200
I don't even dare to kill a chicken,

642
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,840
how can I kill someone?

643
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,070
Right?

644
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:12,990
To tell you the truth,

645
00:30:13,230 --> 00:30:15,640
she was the one
who seduced me that night.

646
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:16,960
I didn't flirt with her.

647
00:30:18,310 --> 00:30:20,030
Sun Caiyun

648
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:21,270
is from the countryside

649
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,920
but she has high standards.

650
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:23,840
She got

651
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,400
Ding Baoyuan,
the manager of the heating station,

652
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:28,400
and she never looked me in the eye.

653
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:30,920
She was the one
who came to me that night.

654
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,200
Sit down.

655
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:40,310
What time did she go to you that night?

656
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:42,600
9:30 PM.

657
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,990
I heard someone knocking on the door,

658
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,160
and I wondered who was looking for me
in the middle of the night.

659
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:47,960
Who's there?

660
00:30:48,710 --> 00:30:49,360
Who?

661
00:30:52,710 --> 00:30:54,360
It's Caiyun.

662
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,840
Why are you here so late?

663
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,310
What are you doing?

664
00:30:59,030 --> 00:30:59,990
I'm ready for bed.

665
00:30:59,990 --> 00:31:01,200
So early?

666
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:03,030
I'm all alone.

667
00:31:03,550 --> 00:31:04,880
You're not going to bed?

668
00:31:06,230 --> 00:31:06,960
Ding

669
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,920
has gone to work.

670
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:09,710
was bored of being alone

671
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:10,750
and came to see you.

672
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:11,840
Come on, let's go to my house.

673
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:12,680
I'll relieve you of your boredom.

674
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,360
I'll relieve you of your boredom.

675
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,990
Your hands are so dirty.

676
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:17,840
Can't you find

677
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:19,990
a cleaner place for me?

678
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:22,990
All right. Why don't we go to Malanhua?

679
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:25,840
Well, go there and take a shower
and wait for me.

680
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:28,070
See you.

681
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:29,790
Don't fool me.

682
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,030
Go now.

683
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:31,960
Promise.

684
00:31:32,230 --> 00:31:33,400
Just go.

685
00:31:36,510 --> 00:31:37,360
Chen,

686
00:31:38,030 --> 00:31:40,510
who wouldn't eat free meat, right?

687
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,710
I got a room

688
00:31:43,030 --> 00:31:45,400
at Malanhua Hotel

689
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:48,440
in our county. It cost me 30 yuan.

690
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:51,030
I asked her over to have some fun.

691
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:53,120
I went to her again in a couple of days,
but she avoided me.

692
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,030
When she got desperate,

693
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,840
she got some thugs to beat me up.

694
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,680
I didn't dare to look for her again.

695
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,160
That's what happened.

696
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,440
Ma Jincai

697
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:09,880
is usually very frugal.

698
00:32:10,310 --> 00:32:12,550
Suddenly, he paid
for a room at my place.

699
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:14,120
I was puzzled.

700
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,360
I asked him, but he didn't tell me.

701
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,640
Not long after he went in,

702
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:22,120
Ding Baoyuan's wife came in

703
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,920
with a scarf covering her face.

704
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:33,710
That's when I knew the two of them
were sleeping together.

705
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:35,960
Someone really doesn't mind.

706
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:38,310
As long as it's not her husband,

707
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,710
it's a good man, huh?

708
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:43,400
Sun Caiyun was the one
who seduced me that night.

709
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,160
I went to her again in a couple of days,
but she avoided me.

710
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:47,510
I went to see Ma Jincai
under the influence of booze.

711
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:50,160
But I looked for him for over an hour
and I couldn't find him.

712
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,510
Since Guan Qiao

713
00:32:51,510 --> 00:32:52,880
has been with Sun Caiyun,

714
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,070
he doesn't need to find a job.

715
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:55,310
Sun Caiyun is keeping him.

716
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:57,840
Are you sure it was that night?

717
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,120
Yes.

718
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:02,360
A person fell out
of the furnace the next day.

719
00:33:02,750 --> 00:33:04,510
That's why I remember it so clearly.

720
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,920
It's scary.

721
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:16,750
[Malanhua]

722
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,160
Chen,

723
00:33:22,030 --> 00:33:22,960
Sun Caiyun

724
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,750
slept with a lecher, Ma Jincai,

725
00:33:24,990 --> 00:33:27,270
in order to trick her husband,
Ding Baoyuan.

726
00:33:27,790 --> 00:33:29,070
What was she thinking?

727
00:33:32,780 --> 00:33:34,710
Because of her lover, Guan Qiao.

728
00:33:35,230 --> 00:33:36,550
She's got a lover, Guan Qiao,

729
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:38,070
and she's still sleeping
with another guy?

730
00:33:38,990 --> 00:33:41,070
There are many reasons
for someone to lie,

731
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:42,640
so why did she have to use this one?

732
00:33:43,550 --> 00:33:44,360
Besides,

733
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:46,310
Ding Baoyuan was fooled
on the first day,

734
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:47,640
but wasn't she afraid of being caught

735
00:33:47,790 --> 00:33:48,960
on the second and third?

736
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:49,880
She wasn't.

737
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:51,680
Why?

738
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,120
Because after they slept together,

739
00:33:57,360 --> 00:33:58,920
Sun Caiyun is at ease.

740
00:33:59,710 --> 00:34:01,920
Turning a lecher into an adulterer.

741
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:05,710
Ma Jincai will definitely
avoid Ding Baoyuan.

742
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,640
What kind of logic is this?

743
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,840
Sun Caiyun's logic.

744
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:16,320
You've lived here for so many years,

745
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,720
what do people here do for a living?

746
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:22,110
Kulu, this small county,

747
00:34:23,070 --> 00:34:24,630
was once rich.

748
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,470
More than a decade ago,

749
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:29,880
there were iron mines in Nanshan.

750
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:35,240
With the mining spree,
the resources were dwindling,

751
00:34:35,720 --> 00:34:37,320
and more and more people were leaving.

752
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:39,470
Those with no skills

753
00:34:39,720 --> 00:34:41,670
stay here and live on fixed wages,

754
00:34:42,110 --> 00:34:44,840
or do a little business or something.

755
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:49,880
This place is so different
from what I imagined.

756
00:34:50,110 --> 00:34:51,030
What did you imagine?

757
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:54,320
Anyway, not like Sun Caiyun.

758
00:34:55,070 --> 00:34:55,880
Ridiculous.

759
00:34:58,070 --> 00:34:59,920
You haven't been here long enough.

760
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,150
Don't you

761
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:11,110
ever think about leaving here?

762
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,110
I'm not capable.

763
00:35:17,900 --> 00:35:19,530
[2004, Kulu County]

764
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:22,030
How's it? Have you made up?

765
00:35:22,190 --> 00:35:24,510
No. My family's falling apart.

766
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:26,670
My wife has taken the kids to the town.

767
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:29,550
If I don't get over there,
I'm going to lose my family.

768
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,320
Master,

769
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:36,760
I heard
that my transfer request was approved,

770
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:38,760
but you didn't sign it.

771
00:35:40,590 --> 00:35:42,280
Why are you leaving?

772
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:44,630
Isn't Kulu your home?

773
00:35:46,150 --> 00:35:48,280
Who's going to do the basic work
when everyone's gone?

774
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:48,800
Yes.

775
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,550
Basic education
for children is important.

776
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:53,110
Is the education here comparable
to that in the town?

777
00:35:53,150 --> 00:35:53,960
No, right?

778
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:56,360
I don't think you're committed
to this case.

779
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,590
Okay, I'll let you go

780
00:36:01,590 --> 00:36:02,630
if we solve this case.

781
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:16,840
Master, you didn't
answer my phone calls,

782
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:19,320
and I can't find you in the office.

783
00:36:19,470 --> 00:36:21,030
You're here sieving dust.

784
00:36:21,990 --> 00:36:23,150
I've changed my shift today.

785
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,470
I just want to be out in the sun.

786
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:27,630
Commissioner Tian came to me again,

787
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:31,720
asking if Ding Baoyuan's case
should be handed over.

788
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:37,400
Hand it over.

789
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,110
Okay.

790
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,070
Do you know

791
00:36:42,720 --> 00:36:44,800
there was a home invasion in Shihe Town?

792
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:46,960
Let's solve this case before you leave.

793
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:57,960
Master,

794
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,550
you promised

795
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:01,880
to sign for me if we solved

796
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:03,110
Ding Baoyuan's case.

797
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:07,190
Yeah, I didn't say
I wouldn't let you go.

798
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:11,760
Jianghe, I can retire anytime.

799
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:13,760
You're doing fine here,

800
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,720
why do you have to go
to a place like that?

801
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:28,110
If you find the right position,

802
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,440
I'll let you go.

803
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:34,320
Remember, the right position.

804
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:37,280
I didn't guide you
for more than ten years

805
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,760
to let you have tea in an office

806
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,960
and read the newspaper.

807
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,920
I'm sure I'll find a suitable position.

808
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,400
Your superior is easy to convince,

809
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:53,760
but ours is not.

810
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,670
Besides, is it right

811
00:37:55,670 --> 00:37:57,720
for a detective
to go into administration?

812
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,920
How long is this temporary?

813
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:03,590
Captain Ge.

814
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,240
I have to go now.

815
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:07,030
Where's the photocopied phone book?

816
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:08,320
Here. Fourth one.

817
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:08,990
This one.

818
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,990
Master, what are you looking for?

819
00:38:12,990 --> 00:38:13,880
Let me help you.

820
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:29,880
Master.

821
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:34,960
Did you see the transfer request
on your desk?

822
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,720
No.

823
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:37,960
That's impossible.

824
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:40,400
I put it here.

825
00:38:45,670 --> 00:38:47,030
Didn't I tell you?

826
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:49,110
You can leave whenever you want

827
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,920
as long as you find the right position.

828
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:15,720
Where is Master?

829
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:17,360
He just got out.

830
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,320
Where to?

831
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:20,590
He left after saying something
about a banquet.

832
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:21,360
Banquet?

833
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,840
He's going to a wedding banquet.

834
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:25,320
Banquet, my foot.

835
00:39:39,150 --> 00:39:41,510
Master, where is the banquet
you are going to?

836
00:39:41,990 --> 00:39:42,800
Chen,

837
00:39:42,990 --> 00:39:44,840
Master left his mobile phone
on his desk.

838
00:39:54,070 --> 00:39:55,990
Master, where are you going?

839
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:57,280
You're in a hurry.

840
00:40:11,470 --> 00:40:12,320
Master!

841
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:16,510
Master!

842
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:30,920
Master!

843
00:40:31,070 --> 00:40:32,760
Stop the car!

844
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:41,760
Master!

845
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:45,400
What's the matter?

846
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:47,880
Master, please sign
this transfer request.

847
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,720
I have an emergency at the moment.

848
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:52,030
So do I. My wife and kids are waiting.

849
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,360
I don't have time to talk to you.

850
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,670
Master, please sign it.

851
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:55,880
Master!

852
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:59,720
You must sign it today.

853
00:41:19,240 --> 00:41:20,030
Chen,

854
00:41:20,590 --> 00:41:21,280
supper for you.

855
00:41:29,660 --> 00:41:32,920
[Sandstorm]

856
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:43,180
[Guan Qiao]

857
00:41:48,580 --> 00:41:54,150
Rain and tears are kissing my face

858
00:41:54,710 --> 00:41:55,600
My wishes seem too far away

859
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:57,760
The coal in Luohe County
has been mined out,

860
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:01,920
and the whole county is being emptied
like a coal seam

861
00:42:02,150 --> 00:42:04,280
that has been drained.

862
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:06,760
The young and strong adults have left.

863
00:42:07,190 --> 00:42:08,400
Those who are capable

864
00:42:08,400 --> 00:42:11,030
take the old and the children with them.

865
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:12,960
Those who aren't capable,

866
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:14,840
leave the old,

867
00:42:15,110 --> 00:42:18,590
the children, the women behind.

868
00:42:19,070 --> 00:42:21,760
They're fleeing in a panic,

869
00:42:21,960 --> 00:42:24,360
without a care in the world.

870
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:28,880
Chun's scared.

871
00:42:29,550 --> 00:42:31,470
She wouldn't have panicked so much

872
00:42:31,470 --> 00:42:33,550
if no one had fled.

873
00:42:34,190 --> 00:42:37,070
When there are many workers coming
to the town,

874
00:42:37,510 --> 00:42:38,990
it's more like paradise

875
00:42:39,150 --> 00:42:42,470
in Chun's eyes.

876
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:45,400
Anyway,

877
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:47,360
suddenly, one day,

878
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,240
the development of Luohe stops

879
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:53,070
and it's about to decline.

880
00:42:53,990 --> 00:42:58,670
The crowds don't come back, but go away.

881
00:42:59,630 --> 00:43:01,110
Chun wants to leave too.

882
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:03,150
Where are all the people?

883
00:43:04,030 --> 00:43:05,590
The provincial capital

884
00:43:06,470 --> 00:43:08,510
is said to be a city

885
00:43:08,510 --> 00:43:10,670
dozens of times bigger than Luohe.

886
00:43:11,630 --> 00:43:13,800
There are towering buildings

887
00:43:13,990 --> 00:43:16,920
and the whole city is growing upwards.

888
00:43:17,590 --> 00:43:19,440
It's not like the pasture and Luohe,

889
00:43:19,550 --> 00:43:22,550
which are flat as far as we can see.

890
00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:26,070
But who can take Chun away?

891
00:43:27,190 --> 00:43:28,920
Since her husband's death,

892
00:43:28,920 --> 00:43:31,150
Chun has fallen out with her in-laws,

893
00:43:31,730 --> 00:43:33,440
and no one can help her.

894
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:35,550
Yes.

895
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:40,510
Who can help her?

896
00:43:42,190 --> 00:43:43,320
Do you love me?

897
00:43:45,510 --> 00:43:46,960
Can you take me away?

898
00:43:49,970 --> 00:43:59,430
To go on, to break free, to run away

899
00:44:19,590 --> 00:44:21,360
What are you looking at?
You want to go too?

900
00:44:21,760 --> 00:44:22,510
No.

901
00:44:35,240 --> 00:44:38,240
The college entrance exams are over.
Why are you still studying?

902
00:44:39,070 --> 00:44:39,720
Do you have any money left?

903
00:44:40,360 --> 00:44:41,360
I'm asking you a question.

904
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:44,510
I don't have any money.

905
00:44:45,440 --> 00:44:46,590
He said he had no money.

906
00:44:47,400 --> 00:44:49,150
In school, the teachers favoured you,

907
00:44:49,150 --> 00:44:51,280
but now that you've graduated,
there's no one to help you.

908
00:44:53,510 --> 00:44:54,590
I really don't have any money on me.

909
00:44:57,470 --> 00:44:58,400
Don't go.

910
00:44:58,760 --> 00:44:59,400
Sit down.

911
00:45:03,510 --> 00:45:04,880
Don't mess about in my place.

912
00:45:07,110 --> 00:45:08,960
Are you upset that we're teasing Fu?

913
00:45:09,590 --> 00:45:10,760
What kind of relationship
do you two have?

914
00:45:11,470 --> 00:45:12,440
What nonsense are you talking about?

915
00:45:16,800 --> 00:45:18,070
Be careful

916
00:45:18,070 --> 00:45:19,550
when you see me again, Fu.

917
00:45:25,320 --> 00:45:27,630
You guys are bullying one.
Aren't you ashamed of yourselves?

918
00:45:27,630 --> 00:45:28,280
Don't run!

919
00:45:29,110 --> 00:45:29,920
Come back!

920
00:45:38,280 --> 00:45:39,070
Here you go.

921
00:45:39,920 --> 00:45:40,400
Wipe it off.

922
00:45:40,400 --> 00:45:41,470
- Thank you.
- Wipe it off.

923
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:43,760
It's not in your eyes, is it?

924
00:45:43,760 --> 00:45:44,400
No.

925
00:45:46,760 --> 00:45:47,400
Take it.

926
00:45:51,240 --> 00:45:52,150
Brat,

927
00:45:53,110 --> 00:45:54,510
you're too honest.

928
00:45:57,720 --> 00:45:59,800
You just won't talk back.

929
00:46:11,110 --> 00:46:12,440
Listen here.

930
00:46:14,240 --> 00:46:15,470
Being too honest

931
00:46:16,880 --> 00:46:18,550
in this world will get you bullied.

932
00:46:34,470 --> 00:46:35,320
Have another bowl.

933
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:38,510
Thank you.

934
00:46:41,030 --> 00:46:43,720
You came to my place
at this time of night.

935
00:46:43,720 --> 00:46:45,070
Doesn't your mum cook for you?

936
00:46:45,960 --> 00:46:47,110
My mum's long dead.

937
00:46:53,280 --> 00:46:54,070
You brat!

938
00:46:59,400 --> 00:47:00,360
I'll wipe it off for you.

939
00:47:01,720 --> 00:47:02,720
No.

940
00:47:03,590 --> 00:47:04,470
What a wimp.

941
00:47:05,360 --> 00:47:06,550
Watch what you do.

942
00:47:12,360 --> 00:47:12,990
Come in.

943
00:47:21,960 --> 00:47:23,320
Come in and wash up.

944
00:48:47,760 --> 00:48:48,800
I'll wipe it for you.

945
00:48:52,800 --> 00:48:53,720
What's your name?

946
00:48:54,960 --> 00:48:55,760
Fu.

947
00:48:58,190 --> 00:48:59,110
How old are you?

948
00:49:01,110 --> 00:49:01,920
20.

949
00:49:10,280 --> 00:49:11,400
What are you staring at?

950
00:49:18,470 --> 00:49:19,280
Towel.

951
00:49:45,690 --> 00:49:50,890
Who's looking for gold?

952
00:49:53,410 --> 00:49:58,760
Who stole the sheep?

953
00:50:01,100 --> 00:50:07,950
The sand slips into my nerves

954
00:50:08,850 --> 00:50:14,160
The world's changes are bothering me

955
00:50:47,560 --> 00:50:53,220
Whose throat has been ripped out
by the wind?

956
00:50:55,300 --> 00:51:01,100
Quicksand, cinders,
who will be cremated?

957
00:51:03,020 --> 00:51:09,320
Whose throat has the wind
ripped out again?

958
00:51:10,710 --> 00:51:18,240
Quicksand, tell me all the answers
